MAN:

11:08.793 --> 11:09.752
What do you know.

11:09.794 --> 11:11.505
Looks like store 617's

11:11.546 --> 11:13.714
actually thinking

11:11.546 --> 11:13.714
about showing up

11:13.756 --> 11:15.509
for the game next week.

