Leave for where?

15:44.318 --> 15:46.279
Kopelman's junkyard.

15:46.320 --> 15:48.406
Reese is going to break

15:46.320 --> 15:48.406
the toilet seat record.

15:48.448 --> 15:49.156
He's what?!

15:49.198 --> 15:50.283
I still have one

15:50.324 --> 15:51.826
you autographed

15:50.324 --> 15:51.826
for my brother.

