15:56.956 --> 15:59.250
Don't think about

15:56.956 --> 15:59.250
what they can do to you.

15:59.292 --> 16:02.420
Just... tell them!

16:15.266 --> 16:18.018
Uh, thank you

16:15.266 --> 16:18.018
for considering me.

16:18.060 --> 16:21.021
It's very flattering.

16:21.063 --> 16:23.942
But I've decided

16:21.063 --> 16:23.942
