Looks like the pit bulls

16:43.503 --> 16:45.212
are herding him

16:43.503 --> 16:45.212
toward the Dobermans.

16:45.254 --> 16:47.548
It's beautiful, really,

16:45.254 --> 16:47.548
the way they work together.

16:47.590 --> 16:49.008
(Reese yelling)

16:50.677 --> 16:52.720
(screams)

16:52.762 --> 16:55.682
Did I make it?

16:52.762 --> 16:55.682
Am I alive?

16:57.183 --> 17:00.060
Why do I have bacon

16:57.183 --> 17:00.060
in my pocket?

17:00.102 --> 17:02.146
Reese, damn it,

17:00.102 --> 17:02.146
you crazy idiot!

17:02.188 --> 17:03.898
Do you know what you are?

17:04.273 --> 17:06.025
You're me!

17:07.109 --> 17:08.736
Mom was right--

17:07.109 --> 17:08.736
we do love trouble.

17:08.778 --> 17:11.781
That's why we do stupid,

17:08.778 --> 17:11.781
moronic things like this.

17:11.823 --> 17:13.073
What are you talking about?

17:13.115 --> 17:14.116
I'm gonna be famous.

17:14.158 --> 17:15.869
This isn't about fame.

17:15.910 --> 17:18.329
It's about putting yourself

17:15.910 --> 17:18.329
in danger for no reason.

17:18.371 --> 17:20.707
It's an addiction

17:18.371 --> 17:20.707
to pain and suffering.

17:20.748 --> 17:22.709
And you know what?

17:20.748 --> 17:22.709
I'm done with it.

17:22.750 --> 17:24.919
And you should be, too,

17:22.750 --> 17:24.919
'cause it isn't worth it.

17:24.961 --> 17:26.086
That's easy for you to say.

17:26.128 --> 17:27.964
You've already had the glory.

17:28.006 --> 17:32.010
Glory? You think this stupid,

17:28.006 --> 17:32.010
dangerous stunt gave me glory?

17:32.051 --> 17:34.261
I'll show you what it gave me.

17:34.303 --> 17:37.097
(boys groaning)

17:37.139 --> 17:39.266
Horrible, isn't it?

17:39.308 --> 17:42.061
Only the middle one's

17:39.308 --> 17:42.061
functional.

17:46.190 --> 17:48.026
I can go now.

17:48.067 --> 17:50.194
I've been set free.

17:50.236 --> 17:52.780
Good-bye and good luck.

17:52.822 --> 17:54.407
BOY:

17:52.822 --> 17:54.407
11, 12...

17:54.448 --> 17:55.575
He got 12!

17:55.616 --> 17:57.117
Reese broke the record!

17:57.159 --> 17:58.828
(boys cheering)

17:58.870 --> 18:00.120
It doesn't matter!

18:00.162 --> 18:03.082
Didn't you people

18:00.162 --> 18:03.082
hear a word I said?

18:04.083 --> 18:06.044
Are you sure he got...

18:06.085 --> 18:07.294
What's the difference?

18:07.336 --> 18:08.713
That's not the point!

18:08.755 --> 18:11.173
What I'm trying to say is...

18:11.966 --> 18:14.802
(groans)

18:17.096 --> 18:18.222
Give me the bacon.

18:18.264 --> 18:21.141
I don't want an asterisk

18:18.264 --> 18:21.141
by my record.

18:23.185 --> 18:25.312
Kid, please,

18:23.185 --> 18:25.312
it's the last inning,

18:25.354 --> 18:28.148
you struck out four times,

18:25.354 --> 18:28.148
dropped six fly balls,

18:28.190 --> 18:31.360
somehow elbowed

18:28.190 --> 18:31.360
yourself in the groin.

18:31.402 --> 18:34.864
The good news is, I think

18:31.402 --> 18:34.864
we're all laughed out.

18:34.906 --> 18:37.450
Just get up there, close

18:34.906 --> 18:37.450
your eyes and swing.

18:37.491 --> 18:39.326
It's because she keeps...

18:39.368 --> 18:41.203
looking at me, on purpose!

18:41.245 --> 18:44.164
She has to be taught

18:41.245 --> 18:44.164
a lesson.

18:44.206 --> 18:47.043
Hey. Your team's

18:44.206 --> 18:47.043
down 16 to one.

18:47.085 --> 18:48.544
Want to get out of here?

18:48.586 --> 18:51.171
Oh, she would just love it

18:48.586 --> 18:51.171
if I did that, wouldn't she?

18:51.213 --> 18:53.173
Well, I'm not gonna give her

18:51.213 --> 18:53.173
the satisfaction.

18:53.215 --> 18:55.175
She's gonna learn

18:53.215 --> 18:55.175
that she can't control me.

18:55.217 --> 18:57.386
You know what, Malcolm,

18:55.217 --> 18:57.386
I don't date guys who are

18:57.428 --> 18:58.679
involved with other women.

18:58.721 --> 19:00.180
Especially when

18:58.721 --> 19:00.180
it's their mother.

19:00.222 --> 19:01.724
Good-bye.

19:06.854 --> 19:10.149
Okay, this is your last chance.

19:13.152 --> 19:14.695
(cell phone ringing)

19:14.737 --> 19:16.196
Hello?

19:16.238 --> 19:18.699
Sure, I got time

19:16.238 --> 19:18.699
