19:18.741 --> 19:20.618
Disagree.

19:28.542 --> 19:30.377
(cheering)

19:30.419 --> 19:32.212
I did it! I hit the ball!

19:32.254 --> 19:34.507
I can't...

19:35.341 --> 19:37.217
Finally! This will show her!

19:37.259 --> 19:38.552
It has to!

19:48.270 --> 19:49.438
Oh, man.

19:49.480 --> 19:51.482
I don't care, I'm going for it.

19:58.489 --> 20:00.116
I'll bet she planned

19:58.489 --> 20:00.116
the whole thing

20:00.158 --> 20:01.241
so it would end up like this.

20:01.283 --> 20:02.952
Now the only way I can score

20:02.994 --> 20:05.454
is if I'm willing to cleat

20:02.994 --> 20:05.454
my own mother in the face.

20:07.373 --> 20:09.249
I can't do it.

20:10.960 --> 20:13.212
What do you know?

20:18.300 --> 20:19.468
He's out!

20:20.553 --> 20:23.263
Honey, if you're

20:20.553 --> 20:23.263
gonna cleat someone,

20:23.305 --> 20:26.350
you have to remember

20:23.305 --> 20:26.350
to lead with your heel.

20:26.392 --> 20:27.935
(whimpers)

20:27.977 --> 20:29.269
FRANCIS:

20:27.977 --> 20:29.269
Didn't you hear me, Piama?

20:29.311 --> 20:31.355
I got 14 toilet seats.

20:31.397 --> 20:33.107
I have the record again.

20:33.149 --> 20:36.318
You know, Mom said this

20:33.149 --> 20:36.318
is exactly how you'd react.

20:36.360 --> 20:38.571
So, I was reading this

20:36.360 --> 20:38.571
really interesting story

20:38.612 --> 20:40.573
about glass eaters...

20:40.614 --> 20:42.200
Nah, you don't want

20:40.614 --> 20:42.200
to hear this.

20:42.241 --> 20:43.784
Dewey, when are

20:42.241 --> 20:43.784
you gonna learn

20:43.826 --> 20:46.286
that I'm the guy who makes

20:43.826 --> 20:46.286
the decisions around here?

20:46.328 --> 20:48.081
Go on.

20:46.328 --> 20:48.081
Well, apparently

20:46.328 --> 20:48.081
the trick is...

20:48.122 --> 20:52.126
Well, that was a pretty shameful

20:48.122 --> 20:52.126
display this afternoon.

20:52.168 --> 20:54.212
Look, I-I was...

20:52.168 --> 20:54.212
It's all right.

20:54.253 --> 20:55.462
I'm not gonna ask you

20:55.504 --> 20:57.506
why you've been behaving

20:55.504 --> 20:57.506
